Subject: How to get the whole Group Probable Owners Report
Description: After we run the Group Probable Owners job and the report gets emailed. We only get 5000 rows. There are many more rows that we can not see. And the app only shows 1000.  Is there a way to get the entire report results?
What_We_Know__c: The customer noticed a limitation in the number of rows in the report.
Solution_Comment__c:
Expand Configure and click Report
Click Configure, and Click the Widgets, and Click Configure
Uncheck the box for "Limit maximum number of display rows."
